{"title":"Camelbak Straps On M.U.L.E. Bikepacking Bags, Fills Stainless & Titanium Podium Bottles!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/camelbak-mule-bikepacking-bags-quickflow-bladder-stainless-titanium-podium-water-bottles/","date":1689094800000,"content":"<p>It seems like it was only a matter of time before Camelbak brought their bag expertise to the world of bikepacking &amp; long-distance gravel. That’s exactly what they brought to Eurobike in their new M.U.L.E. On Bike bag range. However, it was the metal podium bottle on the wall behind the bags that first attracted our attention. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak podium stainless steel bottles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles23.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak podium titanium bottles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles22.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak podium stainless steel bottles\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles21.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For those who prefer a metal bottle to plastic, Camelbak will soon offer their Podium bottle design in Stainless Steel and Titanium. While Camelbak already offered stainless steel bottles in their Everyday collection, this is their first use in the Podium series. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bottles use a dual-wall insulated construction that is said to keep drinks cold for 14-18h. Inside is a flexible straw, however, the straw is the vent, not something you drink out of. If you turn the bottle upside down, water will simply flow out of the valve without needing to suck. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Stainless steel podium bottles will be offered in two sizes, 18 ($35) and 22oz ($40), while Titanium will only be offered in the 18oz size for $100. Yes, a $100 bottle. It <em>is</em> titanium though. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>M.U.L.E. On Bike Bags</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak M.U.L.E. frame bag\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles5.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles6-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak M.U.L.E. seat bag\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles6-297x198.jpg 297w, 