sing at camp. It’s also compatible with the Lifestraw filters, so you can filter the water at camp directly into the bladder. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak M.U.L.E. quick flow bladder\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles18.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles19.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles19-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak M.U.L.E. Quickflow