n\n<p>The bag itself has two sizes and multiple attachment points along three sides so you can place the velcro straps where you need them. Built with a water-repellent fabric and waterproof zippers, the water compartment has two zippers to make it easy to load the bladder, and the other side has a separate pocket for other goods. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are also two sizes of saddle packs with the M.U.L.E. 1 and M.U.L.E. 9, the 9 being the 9L bikepacking variant. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak M.U.L.E. handlebar bag on bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles11.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Camelbak M.U.L.E. handlebar bag open\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles10.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Up front, the M.U.L.E. 12 Handlebar Pack is a cavernous bag to run on your bars. There’s also a M.U.L.E. stem bag with the option to run an additional bottle or have quick access to food or gear. Expect to see these for sale around March 2024, with pricing below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>M.U.L.E. On Bike Pricing:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n<p>M.U.L.E. Frame Pack with Hydration 70oz LG – $150</p>\n\n\n\n<p>M.U.L.E. Frame Pack with Hydration 70oz MD – $140</p>\n\n\n\n<p>M.U.L.E. 12 Handlebar Pack – $100</p>\n\n\n\n<p>M.U.L.E. Stem Bag – $30</p>\n\n\n\n<p>M.U.L.E. 9 Saddle Pack – $90</p>\n\n\n\n<p>M.U.L.E. 1 Saddle Pack – $40</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Quick Stow 2L Reservoir – $50</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>New Chase Vests + Podium Flow 2</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"camelback chase vest race 4\n\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles14.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles16.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Camelbak-Mule-ON-Bike-hydration-bags-bikepacking-steel-titanium-podium-bottles16-800x5